title: Esther Povitsky
itunes:title: Esther Povitsky
description:
Actress and comedian Esther Povitsky (DOLLFACE, SHRILL, iCARLY) is back for a feel good episode where she and Whitney share all their best life hacks. Esther's podcast TRASH TUESDAY is new every Tuesday and DOLLFACE is streaming now on Hulu.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
